NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Stan was also a bit lucky. If I were his partner, I would bid either 4@C or 5@C, using the LOTT. Opposite a pre-empt, from Sandy's perspective, it is unlikely your side has much defense. LOTT always applies when your partner pre-empts. And E/W is at favorable vul (E/W not vul, N/S vul).|
